{"tid":1239642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二百萬人 下星期日見","createTime":"2019-06-18T08:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:19:18.000Z","uid":199631,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6add32e5ec9b3aa0641a8bff34132417a9ce8524","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤回不罷休</span>"},{"pid":"bf770b78ab2b7ad2d38f6cc091deb7ef62b249e6","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"661666cf20041ef1ed1002e53e9f3f32b3f2a833","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e8f15be09a4e39143a65b496df632f7157fad11","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"推撚到林鄭跌落台"},{"pid":"a98208bd346dcb6b7ff0877dba9b5693f81a54f3","tid":1239642,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"推到香港陸沉"},{"pid":"fe750afd563929f2934e7751fcfcf52a711cc32c","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a98208bd346dcb6b7ff0877dba9b5693f81a54f3","tid":1239642,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"推到香港陸沉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"推到你林奠變你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d0158fadfa713d363ced2440e88d30d02d768b","tid":1239642,"uid":262425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"堅持到六月底<br />\n美國總統當勞侵將會在六月底G20峰會跟習近平談香港示威。香港示威已經納入G20侵習會議程。<br />\n美國支持香港反送中示威不是打咀炮，而是實實在在於美國國會立法監察香港人權和自治，懲治和制裁鎮壓示威的中港官員，共和及民主黨議員相繼向中港政府發出警告，押上他們的政治本錢，美國總統亦為香港學生出頭。示威和佔領行動一定要堅持到六月底G20峰會開幕，無論發生甚麼事，一定不要結束。<br />\n林鄭的假道歉全無誠意，政府說沒有將612示威定性為暴動，但是仍然會以暴動罪檢控學生，林鄭不下台，送中惡法只是暫緩。她說暫緩等同撤回，但是並非撤回。這樣的一切，只是想將示威平息下來，讓習近平可以在G20峰會向當勞侵說示威已經和平結束。<br />\n要是示威真的和平結束，美國要支持香港示威亦無能為力。相信中港政府會假讓步真打壓，不要墮入老共的緩兵之計。即使林鄭下台，送中惡法撤回，釋放部份學生，不再鎮壓示威，示威和佔領行動仍然要繼續下去。若果真的在峰會前結束示威，中共和港共會在G20峰會後來個共產黨式清算。<br />\n請各位相信我，示威行動一定要堅持到六月底。"},{"pid":"1797e68e5d41db14fd4ba36f557fd51a3571d506","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fef49dd79c968bf5b28304542d820642c0eae28","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f8d43a962672950e4c93534c7b7061bdce6a9d2","tid":1239642,"uid":50762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eW1PRjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeW1PRjO.png&h=278746ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔洗等到星期日啦屌"},{"pid":"d46ea8920792b00dd0c4ee9640ba1885b4150ea1","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f8d43a962672950e4c93534c7b7061bdce6a9d2","tid":1239642,"uid":50762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eW1PRjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeW1PRjO.png&h=278746ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔洗等到星期日啦屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"咁Chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e597d5687ea4bc25709478be8b60f87adf3486ac","tid":1239642,"uid":258022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6add32e5ec9b3aa0641a8bff34132417a9ce8524","tid":1239642,"uid":199631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤回不罷休</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"0fb83b32258c8c157640cd6965597fade3208453","tid":1239642,"uid":258022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6add32e5ec9b3aa06